First Department,

June, 1965

(June 3, 1965) The People of the State of New York v. Kenny Grier.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted. Under section 517 of the Code of Criminal Procedure no appeal lies to this court from an order denying a motion for a free copy of minutes. (People v. Leggett, 14 A D 2d 708 [2d Dept.].) Concur — Rabin, J. P., Valente, McNally, Eager and Steuer, JJ.
